&lt;h1 id="work-as-hard-as-you-can"&gt;Work As Hard As You Can&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;May 6 2019&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt; Let&amp;rsquo;s talk about hard work. There&amp;rsquo;s a battle that happens on Twitter a lot. Should you work hard or should you not? &lt;strong&gt;David Heinemeier Hansson&lt;/strong&gt; says, &amp;ldquo;It&amp;rsquo;s like you&amp;rsquo;re slave-driving people.&amp;rdquo; &lt;strong&gt;Keith Rabois&lt;/strong&gt; says, &amp;ldquo;No, all the great founders worked their fingers to the bone.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>